show.description: Ye kahani hai ek aisi ladki ki jisne paise ki bhook mein aakar ek pavitra maa bete ke rishte ko bhi buri nazar se dekha aur apni hi shaadi ke din apni hone wale pati ki saas ko bohot torcher kiya.
